This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-python3-yapps2 layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://github.com/smurfix/yapps
  branch: master

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-python3-yapps2 layer as pull requests against the maintainer's git repository:

Maintainer: Peter Den Hartog <https://github.com/pddenhar>


Adding the meta-python3-yapps2 layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-python3-yapps2'

Don't forget to add `python3-yapps2-native` to your DEPENDS if you need the `yapps2` binary copied to `/usr/bin` in your sysroot.

If you only need the Python library, you can add `python3-yapps2`.